(ns farsund.window.subs
  (:require [re-frame.core :as rf]))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/window
  (fn [db _]
    (:window db)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/inner-height
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :inner-height] 0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/inner-width
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :inner-width] 0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/scrolling?
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :scrolling?])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/scroll-top
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :scroll-top] 0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/client-height
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :client-height] 0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/scroll-height
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :scroll-height] 0)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/near-bottom?
  :<- [:window/scroll-height]
  :<- [:window/client-height]
  :<- [:window/scroll-top]
  (fn [[scroll-height client-height scroll-top]]
    (< (- scroll-height client-height scroll-top) 100)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/breakpoint
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:window :breakpoint])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/xs?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (= :xs breakpoint)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/sm?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (= :sm breakpoint)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/<=sm?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:xs :sm} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/>=sm?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:sm :md :lg :xl} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/md?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (= :md breakpoint)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/<=md?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/>=md?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:md :lg :xl} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/lg?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (= :lg breakpoint)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/<=lg?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md :lg} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/>=lg?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:lg :xl} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/xl?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (= :xl breakpoint)))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/<=xl?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md :lg :xl} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/>=xl?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    (boolean (#{:xl} breakpoint))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/gt?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint [_ size]]
    (let [order [:xs :sm :md :lg :xl]]
      (> (.indexOf order breakpoint) (.indexOf order size)))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/ge?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint [_ size]]
    (let [order [:xs :sm :md :lg :xl]]
      (>= (.indexOf order breakpoint) (.indexOf order size)))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/lt?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint [_ size]]
    (let [order [:xs :sm :md :lg :xl]]
      (> (.indexOf order breakpoint) (.indexOf order size)))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/le?
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint [_ size]]
    (let [order [:xs :sm :md :lg :xl]]
      (> (.indexOf order breakpoint) (.indexOf order size)))))


(rf/reg-sub
  :window/breakpoints
  :<- [:window/breakpoint]
  (fn [breakpoint]
    {:breakpoint breakpoint
     :xs?        (= :xs breakpoint)
     :sm?        (= :sm breakpoint)
     :<=sm?      (boolean (#{:xs :sm} breakpoint))
     :>=sm?      (boolean (#{:sm :md :lg :xl} breakpoint))
     :md?        (= :md breakpoint)
     :<=md?      (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md} breakpoint))
     :>=md?      (boolean (#{:md :lg :xl} breakpoint))
     :lg?        (= :lg breakpoint)
     :<=lg?      (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md :lg} breakpoint))
     :>=lg?      (boolean (#{:lg :xl} breakpoint))
     :xl?        (= :xl breakpoint)
     :<=xl?      (boolean (#{:xs :sm :md :lg :xl} breakpoint))
     :>=xl?      (boolean (#{:xl} breakpoint))}))


(rf/reg-sub
  :layout/columns
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:layout :columns])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :layout/gutter
  (fn [db _]
    (get-in db [:layout :gutter])))


(rf/reg-sub
  :layout/gutter.px
  :<- [:layout/gutter]
  (fn [gutter _]
    (str gutter "px")))

(comment
  (rf/subscribe [:layout/gutter])
  "547be5e18d"
  "307b6684d6"
  )
